{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-jsx","path":"/hooks-1/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"ocean.dev"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"9e59c76c-7b79-5666-bc56-c43b95650993","excerpt":"1. useState 렌더링은 함수 컴포넌트의 return을 실행한다음, 이 실행 결과를 이전의 리액트 트리와 비교해 리렌더링이 필요한 부분만 업데이트 한다. 매번 렌더링이 발생될 때 마다 함수는 다시 새롭게 실행되고, 새롭게 실행되는 함수에서 state는 매번 hello로 초기화되므로 아무리 state를 변경해도 다시 초기화 된다. 함수 컴포넌트는 매번…","html":"<h3 id=\"1-useState\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-useState\" aria-label=\"1 useState permalink\" class=\"heading-anchor before\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M6.188 8.719c.439-.439.926-.801 1.444-1.087 2.887-1.591 6.589-.745 8.445 2.069l-2.246 2.245c-.644-1.469-2.243-2.305-3.834-1.949-.599.134-1.168.433-1.633.898l-4.304 4.306c-1.307 1.307-1.307 3.433 0 4.74 1.307 1.307 3.433 1.307 4.74 0l1.327-1.327c1.207.479 2.501.67 3.779.575l-2.929 2.929c-2.511 2.511-6.582 2.511-9.093 0s-2.511-6.582 0-9.093l4.304-4.306zm6.836-6.836l-2.929 2.929c1.277-.096 2.572.096 3.779.574l1.326-1.326c1.307-1.307 3.433-1.307 4.74 0 1.307 1.307 1.307 3.433 0 4.74l-4.305 4.305c-1.311 1.311-3.44 1.3-4.74 0-.303-.303-.564-.68-.727-1.051l-2.246 2.245c.236.358.481.667.796.982.812.812 1.846 1.417 3.036 1.704 1.542.371 3.194.166 4.613-.617.518-.286 1.005-.648 1.444-1.087l4.304-4.305c2.512-2.511 2.512-6.582.001-9.093-2.511-2.51-6.581-2.51-9.092 0z\"/></svg></a>1. useState</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>렌더링은 함수 컴포넌트의 return을 실행한다음, 이 실행 결과를 이전의 리액트 트리와 비교해 리렌더링이 필요한 부분만 업데이트 한다.</li>\n<li>매번 렌더링이 발생될 때 마다 함수는 다시 새롭게 실행되고, 새롭게 실행되는 함수에서 state는 매번 hello로 초기화되므로 아무리 state를 변경해도 다시 초기화 된다.</li>\n<li>함수 컴포넌트는 매번 함수를 실행해 렌더링이 일어나고, 함수 내부의 값은 함수가 실행될 때마다 다시 초기화 된다.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>useState 훅의 결과값은 어떻게 함수가 실행돼도 그 값을 유지하고 있을까?</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>클로저 이용: 어떤 함수 (useState) 내부에 선언된 함수 (setState)가 함수의 실행이 종료된 이후에도 지역변수인 state를 계속 참조할 수 있다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h4 id=\"Lazy-initialization\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#Lazy-initialization\" aria-label=\"Lazy initialization permalink\" class=\"heading-anchor before\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M6.188 8.719c.439-.439.926-.801 1.444-1.087 2.887-1.591 6.589-.745 8.445 2.069l-2.246 2.245c-.644-1.469-2.243-2.305-3.834-1.949-.599.134-1.168.433-1.633.898l-4.304 4.306c-1.307 1.307-1.307 3.433 0 4.74 1.307 1.307 3.433 1.307 4.74 0l1.327-1.327c1.207.479 2.501.67 3.779.575l-2.929 2.929c-2.511 2.511-6.582 2.511-9.093 0s-2.511-6.582 0-9.093l4.304-4.306zm6.836-6.836l-2.929 2.929c1.277-.096 2.572.096 3.779.574l1.326-1.326c1.307-1.307 3.433-1.307 4.74 0 1.307 1.307 1.307 3.433 0 4.74l-4.305 4.305c-1.311 1.311-3.44 1.3-4.74 0-.303-.303-.564-.68-.727-1.051l-2.246 2.245c.236.358.481.667.796.982.812.812 1.846 1.417 3.036 1.704 1.542.371 3.194.166 4.613-.617.518-.286 1.005-.648 1.444-1.087l4.304-4.305c2.512-2.511 2.512-6.582.001-9.093-2.511-2.51-6.581-2.51-9.092 0z\"/></svg></a>Lazy initialization</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>useState에 변수 대신 함수를 넘기는 것</li>\n<li>state가 처음 만들어질 때만 사용되고, 이후에 리렌더링이 발생된다면 함수의 실행은 무시된다.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"cs\"><pre class=\"language-cs\"><code class=\"language-cs\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>state<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> setState<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">useState</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>'<span class=\"token range operator\">..</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>'<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// App 컴포넌트가 처음 구동될 때만 실행되고, 이후 렌더링 시에는 실행되지 않는다.</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>localStorage, sessionStorage에 대한 접근, map, filter, find 같은 배열에 대한 접근, 혹은 초깃값 계산을 위해\n함수 호출이 필요할 때와 같이 무거운 연산을 포함해 실행비용이 많이 드는 경우 사용</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"2-useEffect\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-useEffect\" aria-label=\"2 useEffect permalink\" class=\"heading-anchor before\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M6.188 8.719c.439-.439.926-.801 1.444-1.087 2.887-1.591 6.589-.745 8.445 2.069l-2.246 2.245c-.644-1.469-2.243-2.305-3.834-1.949-.599.134-1.168.433-1.633.898l-4.304 4.306c-1.307 1.307-1.307 3.433 0 4.74 1.307 1.307 3.433 1.307 4.74 0l1.327-1.327c1.207.479 2.501.67 3.779.575l-2.929 2.929c-2.511 2.511-6.582 2.511-9.093 0s-2.511-6.582 0-9.093l4.304-4.306zm6.836-6.836l-2.929 2.929c1.277-.096 2.572.096 3.779.574l1.326-1.326c1.307-1.307 3.433-1.307 4.74 0 1.307 1.307 1.307 3.433 0 4.74l-4.305 4.305c-1.311 1.311-3.44 1.3-4.74 0-.303-.303-.564-.68-.727-1.051l-2.246 2.245c.236.358.481.667.796.982.812.812 1.846 1.417 3.036 1.704 1.542.371 3.194.166 4.613-.617.518-.286 1.005-.648 1.444-1.087l4.304-4.305c2.512-2.511 2.512-6.582.001-9.093-2.511-2.51-6.581-2.51-9.092 0z\"/></svg></a>2. useEffect</h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>컴포넌트가 렌더링 된 후에 어떠한 부수효과를 일으키고 싶을 때 사용하는 훅</strong></p>\n</blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li>'언제' 일어나는지보다 '어떤 상태값'과 함께 실행되는지 살펴보는 것이 중요함</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"cs\"><pre class=\"language-cs\"><code class=\"language-cs\"><span class=\"token function\">useEffect</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token attribute\"><span class=\"token class-name\">props</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">state</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">//  첫번째 인수 = 실행할 부수 효과가 포함된 함수</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 두번째 인수 = 의존성 배열</span></code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"어떻게-의존성-배열이-변경된-것을-알고-실행될까\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%96%B4%EB%96%BB%EA%B2%8C-%EC%9D%98%EC%A1%B4%EC%84%B1-%EB%B0%B0%EC%97%B4%EC%9D%B4-%EB%B3%80%EA%B2%BD%EB%90%9C-%EA%B2%83%EC%9D%84-%EC%95%8C%EA%B3%A0-%EC%8B%A4%ED%96%89%EB%90%A0%EA%B9%8C\" aria-label=\"어떻게 의존성 배열이 변경된 것을 알고 실행될까 permalink\" class=\"heading-anchor before\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M6.188 8.719c.439-.439.926-.801 1.444-1.087 2.887-1.591 6.589-.745 8.445 2.069l-2.246 2.245c-.644-1.469-2.243-2.305-3.834-1.949-.599.134-1.168.433-1.633.898l-4.304 4.306c-1.307 1.307-1.307 3.433 0 4.74 1.307 1.307 3.433 1.307 4.74 0l1.327-1.327c1.207.479 2.501.67 3.779.575l-2.929 2.929c-2.511 2.511-6.582 2.511-9.093 0s-2.511-6.582 0-9.093l4.304-4.306zm6.836-6.836l-2.929 2.929c1.277-.096 2.572.096 3.779.574l1.326-1.326c1.307-1.307 3.433-1.307 4.74 0 1.307 1.307 1.307 3.433 0 4.74l-4.305 4.305c-1.311 1.311-3.44 1.3-4.74 0-.303-.303-.564-.68-.727-1.051l-2.246 2.245c.236.358.481.667.796.982.812.812 1.846 1.417 3.036 1.704 1.542.371 3.194.166 4.613-.617.518-.286 1.005-.648 1.444-1.087l4.304-4.305c2.512-2.511 2.512-6.582.001-9.093-2.511-2.51-6.581-2.51-9.092 0z\"/></svg></a>어떻게 의존성 배열이 변경된 것을 알고 실행될까?</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>함수 컴포넌트는 매번 함수를 실행해 렌더링을 수행한다.</li>\n<li>함수 컴포넌트는 렌더싱 시 마다 고유의 state와 props를 갖고 있다.</li>\n<li>state와 props의 변화 속에서 일어나는 렌더링 과정에서 실행되는 부수효과 함수</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"클린업-함수\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%81%B4%EB%A6%B0%EC%97%85-%ED%95%A8%EC%88%98\" aria-label=\"클린업 함수 permalink\" class=\"heading-anchor before\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M6.188 8.719c.439-.439.926-.801 1.444-1.087 2.887-1.591 6.589-.745 8.445 2.069l-2.246 2.245c-.644-1.469-2.243-2.305-3.834-1.949-.599.134-1.168.433-1.633.898l-4.304 4.306c-1.307 1.307-1.307 3.433 0 4.74 1.307 1.307 3.433 1.307 4.74 0l1.327-1.327c1.207.479 2.501.67 3.779.575l-2.929 2.929c-2.511 2.511-6.582 2.511-9.093 0s-2.511-6.582 0-9.093l4.304-4.306zm6.836-6.836l-2.929 2.929c1.277-.096 2.572.096 3.779.574l1.326-1.326c1.307-1.307 3.433-1.307 4.74 0 1.307 1.307 1.307 3.433 0 4.74l-4.305 4.305c-1.311 1.311-3.44 1.3-4.74 0-.303-.303-.564-.68-.727-1.051l-2.246 2.245c.236.358.481.667.796.982.812.812 1.846 1.417 3.036 1.704 1.542.371 3.194.166 4.613-.617.518-.286 1.005-.648 1.444-1.087l4.304-4.305c2.512-2.511 2.512-6.582.001-9.093-2.511-2.51-6.581-2.51-9.092 0z\"/></svg></a>클린업 함수</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>이벤트를 등록하고 지울 때 사용한다.</li>\n<li>특정 이벤트 핸들러가 무한히 추가되는 것을 방지한다.</li>\n<li>unmount 개념이라기 보다는, 함수 컴포넌트가 리렌더링 됐을 때 의존성 변화가 있었을 당시 이전의 값을 기준으로 실행되는 개념</li>\n<li><strong>콜백에 실행될 때 마다, 이전의 클린업 함수가 존재한다면 그걸 먼저 실행한 뒤 콜백을 실행한다</strong></li>\n<li>따라서 이벤트를 삭제하는 코드를 클린업 함수에 추가하는 것.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"cs\"><pre class=\"language-cs\"><code class=\"language-cs\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>counter<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> setCounter<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">useState</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token return-type class-name\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">handleClick</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\">setCounter</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>prev <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> prev <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token function\">useEffect</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token return-type class-name\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">addMouseEvent</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>counter<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n    window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>'click'<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> addMouseEvent<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// 클린업 함수</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>'clean up'<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> counter<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 이전 counter 값을 참조함</span>\n      window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">removeEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>'click'<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> addMouseEvent<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token attribute\"><span class=\"token class-name\">counter</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>h1<span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>counter<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>h1<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">button</span> onClick<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>handleClick<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token operator\">+</span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>button<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><figure class='gatsby-resp-image-figure' style='margin-bottom: 16px;'>\n    <span class='gatsby-resp-image-wrapper' style='position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 260px; '>\n      <a class='gatsby-resp-image-link' href='/static/fac5289f8ba779f2d934f39dcec63686/d2869/image.png' style='display: block' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>\n    <span class='gatsby-resp-image-background-image' style=\"padding-bottom: 135.88235294117646%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class='gatsby-resp-image-image' alt='콜백에 실행될 때 마다, 이전의 클린업 함수가 존재한다면 그걸 먼저 실행한 뒤 콜백을 실행한다' title='' src='/static/fac5289f8ba779f2d934f39dcec63686/d2869/image.png' srcset='/static/fac5289f8ba779f2d934f39dcec63686/e7570/image.png 170w,\n/static/fac5289f8ba779f2d934f39dcec63686/d2869/image.png 260w' sizes='(max-width: 260px) 100vw, 260px' style='width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;' loading='lazy' decoding='async'>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class='gatsby-resp-image-figcaption'>콜백에 실행될 때 마다, 이전의 클린업 함수가 존재한다면 그걸 먼저 실행한 뒤 콜백을 실행한다</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<h4 id=\"의존성-배열\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%9D%98%EC%A1%B4%EC%84%B1-%EB%B0%B0%EC%97%B4\" aria-label=\"의존성 배열 permalink\" class=\"heading-anchor before\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M6.188 8.719c.439-.439.926-.801 1.444-1.087 2.887-1.591 6.589-.745 8.445 2.069l-2.246 2.245c-.644-1.469-2.243-2.305-3.834-1.949-.599.134-1.168.433-1.633.898l-4.304 4.306c-1.307 1.307-1.307 3.433 0 4.74 1.307 1.307 3.433 1.307 4.74 0l1.327-1.327c1.207.479 2.501.67 3.779.575l-2.929 2.929c-2.511 2.511-6.582 2.511-9.093 0s-2.511-6.582 0-9.093l4.304-4.306zm6.836-6.836l-2.929 2.929c1.277-.096 2.572.096 3.779.574l1.326-1.326c1.307-1.307 3.433-1.307 4.74 0 1.307 1.307 1.307 3.433 0 4.74l-4.305 4.305c-1.311 1.311-3.44 1.3-4.74 0-.303-.303-.564-.68-.727-1.051l-2.246 2.245c.236.358.481.667.796.982.812.812 1.846 1.417 3.036 1.704 1.542.371 3.194.166 4.613-.617.518-.286 1.005-.648 1.444-1.087l4.304-4.305c2.512-2.511 2.512-6.582.001-9.093-2.511-2.51-6.581-2.51-9.092 0z\"/></svg></a>의존성 배열</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>빈 배열인 경우</p>\n<ul>\n<li>최초 렌더링 직후에 실행된 다음부터는 더 이상 실행되지 않는다.</li>\n<li>아무 값도 넘겨주지 않으면 이 때는 의존성 비교할 필요 없이 렌더링이 발생할 때마다 실행됨</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"useEffect-유무의-차이\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#useEffect-%EC%9C%A0%EB%AC%B4%EC%9D%98-%EC%B0%A8%EC%9D%B4\" aria-label=\"useEffect 유무의 차이 permalink\" class=\"heading-anchor before\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M6.188 8.719c.439-.439.926-.801 1.444-1.087 2.887-1.591 6.589-.745 8.445 2.069l-2.246 2.245c-.644-1.469-2.243-2.305-3.834-1.949-.599.134-1.168.433-1.633.898l-4.304 4.306c-1.307 1.307-1.307 3.433 0 4.74 1.307 1.307 3.433 1.307 4.74 0l1.327-1.327c1.207.479 2.501.67 3.779.575l-2.929 2.929c-2.511 2.511-6.582 2.511-9.093 0s-2.511-6.582 0-9.093l4.304-4.306zm6.836-6.836l-2.929 2.929c1.277-.096 2.572.096 3.779.574l1.326-1.326c1.307-1.307 3.433-1.307 4.74 0 1.307 1.307 1.307 3.433 0 4.74l-4.305 4.305c-1.311 1.311-3.44 1.3-4.74 0-.303-.303-.564-.68-.727-1.051l-2.246 2.245c.236.358.481.667.796.982.812.812 1.846 1.417 3.036 1.704 1.542.371 3.194.166 4.613-.617.518-.286 1.005-.648 1.444-1.087l4.304-4.305c2.512-2.511 2.512-6.582.001-9.093-2.511-2.51-6.581-2.51-9.092 0z\"/></svg></a>useEffect 유무의 차이</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"cs\"><pre class=\"language-cs\"><code class=\"language-cs\"><span class=\"token return-type class-name\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">Component</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>'렌더링 됨'<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token return-type class-name\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">Component</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">useEffect</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>'렌더링됨'<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>useEffect는 <code class=\"language-text\">클라이언트 사이드</code>에서 실행되는 것을 보장함</p>\n<ul>\n<li>따라서 내부에서 <strong>window 객체 접근하는 코드</strong>를 사용해도 됨</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>useEffect는 <strong>컴포넌트 렌더링이 완료된 이후</strong>에 실행됨 -> 성능에 영향 X</p>\n<ul>\n<li>1번의 경우 컴포넌트 렌더링 도중 실행됨</li>\n<li>서버사이드 렌더링의 경우 서버에서도 실행됨</li>\n<li>이 작업은 함수 컴포넌트의 반환을 지연시키는 행위임</li>\n<li>즉 무거운 작업인 경우 렌더링을 방해하므로 성능에 악영향</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"주의할-점\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%A3%BC%EC%9D%98%ED%95%A0-%EC%A0%90\" aria-label=\"주의할 점 permalink\" class=\"heading-anchor before\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M6.188 8.719c.439-.439.926-.801 1.444-1.087 2.887-1.591 6.589-.745 8.445 2.069l-2.246 2.245c-.644-1.469-2.243-2.305-3.834-1.949-.599.134-1.168.433-1.633.898l-4.304 4.306c-1.307 1.307-1.307 3.433 0 4.74 1.307 1.307 3.433 1.307 4.74 0l1.327-1.327c1.207.479 2.501.67 3.779.575l-2.929 2.929c-2.511 2.511-6.582 2.511-9.093 0s-2.511-6.582 0-9.093l4.304-4.306zm6.836-6.836l-2.929 2.929c1.277-.096 2.572.096 3.779.574l1.326-1.326c1.307-1.307 3.433-1.307 4.74 0 1.307 1.307 1.307 3.433 0 4.74l-4.305 4.305c-1.311 1.311-3.44 1.3-4.74 0-.303-.303-.564-.68-.727-1.051l-2.246 2.245c.236.358.481.667.796.982.812.812 1.846 1.417 3.036 1.704 1.542.371 3.194.166 4.613-.617.518-.286 1.005-.648 1.444-1.087l4.304-4.305c2.512-2.511 2.512-6.582.001-9.093-2.511-2.51-6.581-2.51-9.092 0z\"/></svg></a>주의할 점</h4>\n<p><strong>1. react-hooks/exhaustive-deps ESLint 룰을 무시하지 말 것</strong></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"cs\"><pre class=\"language-cs\"><code class=\"language-cs\"><span class=\"token return-type class-name\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">Component</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>log<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n <span class=\"token function\">useEffect</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\">logging</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>log<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// eslint-disable-next-line react-hooks/exhaustive-deps</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>주로 컴포넌트를 마운트하는 시점에만 뭔가 하고 싶을 때 사용</li>\n<li>\n<p>log가 최초로 props로 넘어와서 컴포넌트가 최초로 렌더링 된 시점에만 실행된다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>log가 아무리 변해도 부수효과 실행 안될 수 있음</li>\n<li>따라서 logging은 부모컴포넌트에서 실행되는 것이 옳을 것.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>변경시점을 피할 목적이라면 메모이제이션을 적절히 활용하거나, 적당한 실행위치를 고려해야함</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>2. useEffect의 첫번째 인수에 함수명을 부여하라</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>목적을 명확히 하게 된다.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"cs\"><pre class=\"language-cs\"><code class=\"language-cs\"><span class=\"token function\">useEffect</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n  <span class=\"token return-type class-name\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">logActiveUser</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\">logging</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>user<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>id<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token attribute\"><span class=\"token class-name\">user<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>id</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><strong>3. 거대한 useEffect를 만들지 마라</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>useEffect는 의존성 배열을 바탕으로 렌더링 시 의존성이 변경될 때마다 부수 효과를 실행.</li>\n<li>이 부수 효과의 크기가 커질수록 애플리케이션 성능에 악영향</li>\n<li>적은 수의 의존성 배열을 사용하도록 변경</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>4. 불필요한 외부 함수를 만들지 마라</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>useEffect 내에서 사용할 부수효과라면 내부에서 만들어서 정의해서 사용하는 편이 훨씬 도움이 된다.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>5. useEffect의 콜백 인수로 비동기 함수를 바로 넣지 않는다.</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>비동기로 함수를 호출할 경우 state의 경쟁상태를 야기할 수 있다.</li>\n<li>cleanup 함수의 실행순서도 보장할 수 없다.</li>\n<li>다만 async await 함수를 선언해 실행하거나, 함수를 만들어서 사용하는 것은 가능하다.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"cs\"><pre class=\"language-cs\"><code class=\"language-cs\"><span class=\"token comment\">// Effect callbacks are synchronous to prevent race conditions. Put the async function inside:</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">useEffect</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">async</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> response <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">await</span> <span class=\"token function\">fetch</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>'https<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>jsonplaceholder<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>typicode<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>com<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>todos<span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span>'<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> data <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">await</span> response<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">json</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>data<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"cs\"><pre class=\"language-cs\"><code class=\"language-cs\">  <span class=\"token function\">useEffect</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">async</span> <span class=\"token return-type class-name\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">fetchData</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> response <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">await</span> <span class=\"token function\">fetch</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>'https<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>jsonplaceholder<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>typicode<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>com<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>todos<span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span>'<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> json <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">await</span> response<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">json</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>json<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"title":"3-1. useState, useEffect","date":"September 03, 2024","update":"September 03, 2024","tags":["React"],"series":"모던 리액트 Deep Dive"},"fields":{"slug":"/hooks-1/","readingTime":{"minutes":8.01}}},"seriesList":{"edges":[{"node":{"id":"b25633cf-f44b-5f9a-969e-7bc1194f5006","fields":{"slug":"/react-js-1/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"1.1. [JS] 동등비교, 함수, 클래스, 클로저"}}},{"node":{"id":"81cb746f-b6ec-58e2-aa5f-10fc1af0cb82","fields":{"slug":"/react-js-2/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"1.2. [JS] 이벤트루프와 비동기통신, JS 문법, 타입스크립트 "}}},{"node":{"id":"aa42a09b-5b16-52b8-9e72-6d9c9417b078","fields":{"slug":"/\bjsx/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"2.1 JSX가 트랜스파일을 거쳐 자바스크립트 코드로 변환되는 과정"}}},{"node":{"id":"f178f4cf-1b41-5f1b-b38c-ebebd897f3d8","fields":{"slug":"/react-rendering/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"2.2 리액트 렌더링 과정"}}},{"node":{"id":"9e59c76c-7b79-5666-bc56-c43b95650993","fields":{"slug":"/hooks-1/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"3-1. useState, useEffect"}}},{"node":{"id":"cadd6c70-6957-56f4-a1f7-3a15dad5d766","fields":{"slug":"/hooks-2/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"3-2. useMemo, useCallback, useRef, useLayoutEffect"}}},{"node":{"id":"3b642a79-a0c9-5cb1-b049-1d15ff16eedd","fields":{"slug":"/usehooks-hoc/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"3-3. 사용자 정의 훅과 고차 컴포넌트 중 무엇을 써야 할까?"}}},{"node":{"id":"10541b16-ba35-5bec-8cdc-a584da03ee98","fields":{"slug":"/ssr/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"4-1. 서버 사이드 렌더링"}}},{"node":{"id":"12fea60c-44e2-5dcb-911a-3dda4a2e1bc9","fields":{"slug":"/ssr-apis/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"4-2. 서버 사이드 렌더링을 위한 리액트 API"}}},{"node":{"id":"2a65f3a7-c813-5ef8-924e-c89a248be49f","fields":{"slug":"/nextjs/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"4-3. Next.js 톺아보기 [wip]"}}}]},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/react-rendering/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"2.2 리액트 렌더링 과정"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/hooks-2/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"3-2. useMemo, useCallback, useRef, useLayoutEffect"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"9e59c76c-7b79-5666-bc56-c43b95650993","series":"모던 리액트 Deep Dive","previousPostId":"f178f4cf-1b41-5f1b-b38c-ebebd897f3d8","nextPostId":"cadd6c70-6957-56f4-a1f7-3a15dad5d766"}},"staticQueryHashes":[],"slicesMap":{}}